Package: descriptiveStats
Title: Descriptive Statistics Functions for Numeric Vectors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Your",
           family = "Name",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "your.email@example.com")
Description: A lightweight collection of descriptive statistics functions
    including mean, median, mode, first quartile, third quartile, and
    interquartile range. Functions handle edge cases such as empty vectors,
    NA values, and ties in mode calculations, providing informative error
    messages for invalid inputs.
